He/him.

Musician living outside Galway with my boyfriend and our dog. Plays piano and write songs and instrumental music. Particularly likes arranging strings and voices.

Currently working remotely in a tech so I can pay for things and eat. I've been working remotely in this role for 8 years, and hybrid while self-employed for the previous 12 years.

Enjoys nature, supporting small local business, LGBTQ+ advocacy, making food, and have become an accidental gardener.
